#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "&sheets; Basics"
msgstr "&sheets; Osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Like the rest of &kde;, &sheets; is highly configurable, which can cause "
"problems for readers trying to compare the text in a document such as this "
"with what they see on the version of &sheets; running on their desktop. To "
"cut down on some of the possibilities for confusion, it is suggested that "
"when you first start to use &sheets; you set the default options in all "
"pages of the &sheets; configuration dialog (obtained by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Sheets...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Kao i ostatak &kde;, &sheets;  ima mnogo podešavanja, što može uzrokovati "
"probleme korisnicima koji žele da uporede tekstove u dokumentima kao što je "
"ovaj sa onim što vide u &sheets; koji je pokrenut na njihovom desktopu. Da "
"bi se smanjila mogućnost zabune, preporučuje se da se pri prvom korištenju "
"&sheets;  podese zadane postavke za sve stranice &sheets; u konfiguracijskom "
"okviru(pristupa mu se na slijedeći način <menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Podesi listove...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> )."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spreadsheets for Beginners"
msgstr "Tabele za početnike"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section attempts to explain by example what a spreadsheet program such "
"as &sheets; actually does, and why it is such a useful tool in any situation "
"where you have to deal with numbers. If you have already used a spreadsheet "
"program you may wish to skip to the next section."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj odjeljak pokušava objasniti, pomoću primjera, šta program kao &sheets;  "
"zapravo radi, i zašto je tako koristan alat u bilo kojoj situaciji u kojoj "
"se radi sa brojevima. Ako ste već koristili tabelarni program možda želite "
"preskočiti na slijedeći dio."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:34
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The first thing to do is to start up &sheets;. You can do this by "
#| "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on a &sheets; icon if there is "
#| "one on your desktop or panel, or you can select "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Office</guimenu><guimenuitem>&sheets;</guimenuitem> "
#| "</menuchoice> from the &kmenu;."
msgid ""
"The first thing to do is to start up &sheets;. You can do this by "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on a &sheets; icon if there is one "
"on your desktop or panel, or you can select <menuchoice><guimenu>Office</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&sheets;</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from the "
"application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Prvo treba pokrenuti &sheets;. To možete uraditi na slijedeći način "
"<mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> klik na &sheets; ikonu na vašem desktopu "
"ili ploči, ili odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Office</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>&sheets;</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> iz &kmenu;."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "&sheets; at first run"
msgstr "&sheets; pri prvom pokretanju"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When it has started you will be given the choice of opening a recent "
"document, creating a new document from a template (with templates "
"categories) or opening an existing document . Select the <guilabel>General</"
"guilabel> category on the left and choose the <guilabel>Blank Worksheet</"
"guilabel> template. Then click the <guibutton>Use This Template</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Kada je pokrenut biće vam ponuđeno nekoliko opcija, otvaranje nedavno "
"otvaranog dokumenta, kreiranje novog dokumenta iz šablona(sa kategorijama "
"šablona) ili otvaranje postojećeg dokumenta . Odaberite <guilabel>Opšte</"
"guilabel> kategoriju sa lijeve strane i odaberite <guilabel>Prazna Radna "
"sveska</guilabel> šablon. Zatim pritisnite <guibutton>Koristi ovaj šablon</"
"guibutton>  tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Looking at &sheets; once it has started up, you will see a sheet of empty "
"rectangular cells arranged in numbered rows and lettered columns. This is "
"where you enter data or formula, text or charts."
msgstr ""
"Posmatrajući &sheets;  jednom kad je pokrenut, vidjećete stranicu sa praznim "
"pravougaonicima poredanim po brojevima redova i slovima u kolonama. To j "
"eprostor u koji unosite podatke,  formule, tekst, tabele."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot starting1"
msgstr "Početni izgled ekrana1"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now, enter the text and values shown in the first 5 rows of the above "
"screenshot into the same cells of your spreadsheet. Ignore what is in row 7 "
"for the moment. To enter anything into a cell first select the cell by "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking inside it, then type whatever you "
"want, then press &Enter; or use the arrow keys to move the selection point "
"to another cell."
msgstr ""
"Sada unesite tekst i vrijednosti u prvih pet redova u ekranu iznad  u iste "
"ćelije u vašoj radnoj svesci.Ignorišite ono što je u sedmom redu u ovo "
"trenutku. Da biste bilo šta unijeli u ćeliju, prvo odaberite ćeliju "
"<mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> klikom unutar nje, zatim upišite bilo šta, "
"i pritisnite &Enter; ili koristite strelice da se prebacite u drugu ćeliju."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What we have entered so far could be a simple budget for the next two "
"months, listing how much we think we will be spending for Food, Shelter, "
"Clothing and any Other expenditure. Now select cell B7 (column B, row 7), "
"type in <userinput>=B2+B3+B4+B5</userinput> and press &Enter;. Because it "
"begins with a <keycap>=</keycap> symbol &sheets; sees this as a formula, "
"something it has to calculate, in this case by adding together the values in "
"the 4 cells B2 to B5, and what is shown in the cell B7 is the result of that "
"calculation."
msgstr ""
"Ono što smo unijeli dosad može biti jednostavan budžet za naredna dva "
"mjeseeca, sa prikazom koliko mmislimo potrošiti na hranu, dom, odjeću i "
"ostale troškove. Sada odaberite ćeliju B7 (kolona B, red 7), unesite "
"<userinput>=B2+B3+B4+B5</userinput> i pritisnite &Enter;. Zbog toka što "
"počinje sa <keycap>=</keycap> simbolom &sheets; vidi ovo kao formulu, nešto "
"što mora izračunati, u ovom slučaju sabrati vrijednosti u 4 ćelije  B2 do "
"B5, a ono što je prikazano u B7 je rezultat računanja."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You could enter a similar formula into cell C7, except that in this case it "
"would have to be <userinput>=C2+C3+C4+C5</userinput>, but there is an easier "
"way which is to Copy cell B7 and Paste it into C7. &sheets; will "
"automatically adjust the cell references from B.. to C.. when the Paste is "
"done."
msgstr ""
"Sličnu formulu možete unijeti u C7, osim što u ovom slučaju to izgleda ovako "
"<userinput>=C2+C3+C4+C5</userinput>, ali postoji i lakši način da se kopira "
"ćelija B7 i zalijepi u ćeliju C7. &sheets; će automatski podesiti reference "
"ćelije B.. u C.. kada je lijepljenje gotovo."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At this point you may think that &sheets; is doing no more than you could "
"manage with pencil, paper and a calculator, and you could be right, but "
"remember that this is a very small example of a spreadsheet, doing simple "
"calculations on only a few numbers. For any reasonably amount of values or "
"data using a spreadsheet to do the calculations is much quicker and more "
"accurate than doing them manually."
msgstr ""
"Možte pomisliti da  &sheets; ne radi ništa sto se na bi moglo uraditi sa "
"olovkom papirom i kalkulatorom, i možda su u pravu, ali zapamtite da veoma "
"mali dio radne sveske radi jednostavna računanja sa malo brojeva. Za razumnu "
"količinu vrijednosti i podataka korištenje radne sveske za računanje je puno "
"brže i tačnije nego računanje ručno."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also, a spreadsheet lets you play the <quote>What if?</quote> game. Because "
"each formula is automatically recalculated whenever any of the values it "
"refers to are changed, you can quickly see what happens if you alter any of "
"them. Using our example you can see the effect of reducing the amount spent "
"on food in December by just entering a new value into cell C2. If you had a "
"spreadsheet that modelled the greenhouse effect accurately you could perhaps "
"see the effect of a 50 percent reduction in the amount of methane released "
"into the atmosphere."
msgstr ""
"Radna sveska vam omogućava i igranje <quote>Šta ako?</quote> igre. Kako je "
"svaka formula ponovo proračunata svaki put kada se promjeni neka vrijednost "
"koja učestvuje u proračunu, možete brzo uočiti šta se dešava pri promjeni "
"neke od njih. Koristeći naš primjer moćete uočiti šta se dešava ako smanjite "
"količinu potrošenu na hranu u decembru samo ako unesete novu vrijednost u "
"ćeliju C2.Ako imate ćeliju koja modelira efekat staklenika precizno, možete "
"na primjer vidjeti efekat 50% smanjenja emisije metana u atmosferu."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Cells"
msgstr "Odabiranje ćelija"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select a single cell or a rectangular area of cells in the "
"spreadsheet. The selected cell(s) are displayed with a thick black border."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati jednu ćeliju ili pravougaonu oblast ćelija u radnom listu. "
"Odabrane ćelije se prikazuju kao blijedo označen okvir."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can select a single cell in one of the following ways"
msgstr "Jednu ćeliju možete odabrati na slijedeće načine"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on it"
msgstr "<mousebutton>lijevo</mousebutton> klikom na nju"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"enter the cell reference (for example <userinput>B5</userinput>) into the "
"cell reference box at the left end of the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> "
"tool options and press &Enter;"
msgstr ""
"unesite referencu ćelije (na primjer <userinput>B5</userinput>) u okvir sa "
"referencom ćelije <guilabel>Uređivanje ćelije</guilabel> alatnu opciju i "
"pritisnite &Enter;"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Goto Cell...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu option"
msgstr ""
"koristite <menuchoice><guimenu>Idi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Idi na ćeliju...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> meni opciju"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also steer your way around with the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys. "
"Pressing the &Enter; key will move the current selection one position up, "
"down, left or right depending on the setting in the <guilabel>Interface</"
"guilabel> page of &sheets;'s <link linkend=\"configinterface\">configuration "
"dialog box</link>."
msgstr ""
"Možete se pomjerati po radnom listu korištenjem <keysym>strelica</keysym> . "
"Pritiskanjem &Enter; tipke će pomjeriti trenutno selektovanu ćeliju gore "
"dolje lijevo ili fesno zavisno od postavki u <guilabel>Interfejs</guilabel> "
"stranici &sheets;'a <link linkend=\"configinterface\">konfiguracijski radni "
"okvir</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;</keycombo> key down while "
"using the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys the selection will move to the start "
"or end of the block of occupied cells."
msgstr ""
"Ako pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;</keycombo> tipku dok "
"koristite <keysym>strelica</keysym> tipke označeno područje će se pomjeriti "
"na kraj ili početak bloka zauzetih ćelija."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select an area of contiguous cells drag the mouse cursor across the "
"desired area with the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> button held down, or "
"enter the references of the top left and bottom right cells separated by a "
"colon into the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> cell reference box (for "
"example <userinput>B7:C14</userinput>) and press &Enter;, or enter these "
"cell references in a similar format into the dialog box brought up by "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Goto Cell...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Da odaberete područje susjednih ćelija prevucite pokazivač miša preko "
"željenog područja sa pritisnutom <mousebutton>lijevom</mousebutton> tipkom "
"miša, ili unesite referencu gornje lijeve i donje desne ćelije odvojene "
"zarezom u <guilabel>Uređivač ćelija</guilabel> okvir za referencu ćelije (na "
"primjer <userinput>B7:C14</userinput> ) i pritisnite &Enter;, ili unesite "
"ove reference ćelija u sličnom formatu u ovir koji se pojavi pri odabiru "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Idi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Idi na ćeliju...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select an area of cells by selecting the cell in one corner of "
"the wanted area then holding the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; </"
"keycombo> key down while using the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse "
"button to select the cell in the opposite corner."
msgstr ""
"Također možete odabrati područje ćelija odabranjem ćelije u jednom uglu "
"željenog područja i držanjem <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; </keycombo> "
"tipke pritisnutom dok koristite <mousebutton>lijevu</mousebutton> tipku miša "
"da odaberete ćeliju u suprotnom uglu."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select non-contiguous cells, click on the first cell you want to select "
"then hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> key and select "
"the other cells."
msgstr ""
"Da odaberete ne susjedne ćelije, pritisnite na prvu ćeliju koju želite "
"odabrati i držite  <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> tipku i "
"odaberite ostale ćelije."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a complete row or column of cells <mousebutton>left </mousebutton> "
"click on the row number at the left of the worksheet or on the column "
"letters at the top. To select adjacent rows or columns drag the mouse "
"pointer over the appropriate row numbers or column letters with the "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> button held down."
msgstr ""
"Da odaberete cijeli red ili kolonu ćelija <mousebutton>lijevom </"
"mousebutton> tipkom miša pritisnite na broj reda u lijevom dijelu radnog "
"lista ili na slovo kolone na vrhu. Da odaberete spojene redove ili kolone "
"prevucite pokazivač miša preko željenog broja reda ili slova kolone sa "
"<mousebutton>lijevom</mousebutton> tipkom miša pritisnutom."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select non-contiguous rows or columns of cells, click on the first row "
"number or column letter then hold the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</"
"keycombo> key and select the other rows or columns of cells."
msgstr ""
"Da odaberete ne susjedne ćelije, pritisnite na prvi broj reda ili slova "
"kolone i onda držite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> tipku i "
"odaberite ostale redove i kolone ćelija."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering Data"
msgstr "Unos podataka"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering data into a cell can be as simple as selecting the cell, typing "
"your data, then pressing &Enter; or moving the selection to another cell "
"with one of the <keysym>arrow</keysym> keys. Depending on how you enter the "
"data, &sheets; will interpret it as a number, date, time or text:"
msgstr ""
"Unos podataka u ćeliju može biti jednostavan kao odabiranje ćeije tipkanje "
"podataka i onda pritiskanja tipke  &Enter; ili pomjeranja odabira na drugu "
"ćeliju sa jednom od <keysym>strelica</keysym>. Zavisno od unosa podataka "
"&sheets; ih interpretira kao brojeve, datum, vrijeme ili tekst:"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Numbers are entered in the obvious way; <userinput>123</userinput>, "
"<userinput> -123</userinput>, <userinput>456.7</userinput> or in scientific "
"notation <userinput>-1.2E-5</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Brojevi se unose na očigledan način; <userinput>123</userinput>, <userinput> "
"-123</userinput>, <userinput>456.7</userinput> ili na u naučnom zapisu "
"<userinput>-1.2E-5</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dates should be entered in your <quote>System</quote> format, as defined in "
"the &systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu> "
"Country/Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date &amp; Time</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> tab. If, for example, you are using the DD/MM/"
"YYYY form you should enter <userinput>30/03/2012</userinput> for 30th March "
"2012. Leading zeroes can be omitted from the day and month fields and only "
"the last one or two digits of the year need to be entered if the date is in "
"the current century, for example <userinput>9/1/9</userinput> for 9th "
"January 2009."
msgstr ""
"Datum bi trebao biti unijet u <quote>Sistemskom formatu</quote> u "
"&systemsettings; u <menuchoice><guimenu>Lockalno</guimenu> <guisubmenu> "
"Zemlja/Region &amp; jezik</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Datum &amp; vrijeme</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> kartici. Ako na primjer koristite DD/MM/GGGG "
"format trebate unijeti  <userinput>30/03/2012</userinput> za 30. mart 2012. "
"Nula može biti izostavljena na početku dana i mejseca sa jednocifrenim "
"brojevima u zapisu, ili za godinu u trenutnom stoljeću dovoljno je unijeti "
"dva zadnja broja, na primjer <userinput>9/1/9</userinput> za 9. januar 2009."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Times should also be entered using the <quote>System</quote> format. For "
"example if you are using a 12 hour clock then enter times in HH:MIN am|pm or "
"HH:MIN:SS am|pm format such as <userinput>9:42 am</userinput> or <userinput> "
"10:30:52 pm</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Vrijeme bi također trebalo biti unijeto korištenjem  <quote>Sistemskog</"
"quote> formata. Na primjer ako koristite 12 satni sat onda unosite vrijeme "
"kao  HH:MIN am|pm ili HH:MIN:SS am|pm formati kao  <userinput>9:42 am</"
"userinput> ili <userinput> 10:30:52 pm</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; defines any input data as <quote>text</quote> if it cannot "
"recognize the data as being a number, date or time."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; definira sve ulazne podatke kao <quote>tekst</quote> ako ne može "
"odrediti da li su podaci brojevi, datum ili vrijeme."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, &sheets; right justifies numbers, dates and times within a cell "
"and left justifies anything else. This can be a useful guide to whether you "
"have entered a date or time in the correct format. But remember that how "
"items are displayed can be changed by altering the <link linkend=\"formatdata"
"\">cell format</link>."
msgstr ""
"Zadano &sheets; desno poravnjava brojeve datume i vrijeme unutar ćelije, a "
"lijevo sve ostalo. Ovo može biti korisno za provjeru da li ste pravilno "
"unijeli datum ili vrijeme. Zapamtite da način prikaza stavki može biti "
"promijenjen promjenom <link linkend=\"formatdata\">formata ćelije</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main text entry box in the <guilabel>Cell Editor</guilabel> tool options "
"provides an easy way of editing the contents of a selected cell. Press "
"&Enter; or <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on the green tick mark when "
"you are happy with what you have entered, or click on the red cross to "
"cancel your edits."
msgstr ""
"Glavni okvir za unos teksta u  <guilabel>Uređivač ćelije</guilabel> alatnoj "
"opciji omogućav lagan način uređivanja sadržaja odabranih ćelija. Pritisnite "
"&Enter; ili <mousebutton>lijevom</mousebutton>  tipkom miša na zelenu oznaku "
"kada ste zadovoljni unosom, ili na crveni križić da poništite uređivanje."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic Cell Format"
msgstr "Generičko formatiranje ćelije"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; uses the <quote>Generic</quote> cell format as default. As long as "
"this format is used, &sheets; autodetects the actual data type depending on "
"the current cell data. For example if you enter some text into a cell and "
"later enter a number into the same cell, &sheets; automatically interprets "
"the new data as a number. If you want to define the type of data yourself, "
"you can explicitly set it in the <link linkend=\"formatdata\">cell format</"
"link>. You can change the format back to <quote>Generic</quote> at any time."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; koristi <quote>Generički</quote> format ćelija kao zadani. Sve dok "
"je ovo formatiranje korišteno, &sheets; automatski detektuje stvarni tip "
"podataka zavisno od trenutnih podataka u ćeliji. Na primjer ako unesete dio "
"teksta u ćeliju i a kasnije broj u neku ćeliju, &sheets; automatski "
"interpretira novi podatak kao broj. Ako želite definisati vlastiti tip "
"podataka, možete ga eksplicitno postaviti u <link linkend=\"formatdata"
"\">foramtiranje ćelije</link>. Format možete promijeniti u <quote>Generički</"
"quote> u bilo kom trenutku."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy, Cut and Paste"
msgstr "Kopiraj, izreži i zalijepi"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At first glance, &sheets;'s <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> appear "
"to be similar to these functions in other &kde; applications. Having "
"selected a cell or cells, you can choose <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu or from "
"the drop down menu you get by holding the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button down on a selected cell. You can also use the shortcuts "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo> or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap> </keycombo>, then move the "
"selection to the target cell and choose <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> or "
"press <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>. "
"However there are some subtleties associated with these functions in "
"&sheets; and these are discussed below."
msgstr ""
"Na prvi pogled, &sheets;-ov <guimenuitem>Isjeci</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem>Zalijepi</guimenuitem> su "
"slični kao i u ostalim &kde; aplikacijama. Kada odaberete ćeliju ili ćelije "
"možete odabrati <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Isjeci</"
"guimenuitem> iz <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> menija ili iz padajućeg menija koji "
"se pojavi kada držite <mousebutton>desnu</mousebutton> tipku miša "
"pritisnutom na odabranoj ćeliji. Možete koristiti i kratice <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo> ili <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap> </keycombo>, onda se premjestite na željenu "
"ćeliju i odaberite <guimenuitem>Zalijepi</guimenuitem> ili pritisnite "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>. Kako god "
"postoje neke nejasnoće povezane sa ovimfunkcijama u &sheets;, o njima je "
"diskutovano u nastavku."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a cell contains a formula then the formula itself is copied rather than "
"the displayed result, and if the formula contains a reference to another "
"cell, then that reference is changed by the <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> "
"or <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> "
"operation to point to the cell that is in the same relative position as in "
"the original cell. For example if cell A2 contains the formula <userinput> "
"=B3</userinput> and is copied to C4, cell C4 will contain <userinput>=D5 </"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Ako ćelija sadrži formulu onda je formula radije kopirana umjesto prikazanog "
"rezultata, i ako formula sadrži referencu na neku ćeliju, ta referenca je "
"promijenjena unutar <guimenuitem>Isjeci</guimenuitem> ili "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem>Zalijepi</guimenuitem> "
"operacija da pokazuje na ćeliju na istoj poziciji u odnosu na originalnu "
"ćeliju. Na primjer ako ćelija A2 sadrži formulu <userinput> =B3</userinput> "
"i kopiramo je u ćeliju C4, ćelija C4 sadrži <userinput>=D5 </userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This may seem to be a rather strange way of doing a copy, but 99 percent of "
"the time it is exactly what is wanted (if it is not then see the section "
"about <link linkend=\"absolute\">absolute cell references</link>). For "
"example in the simple shopping list shown below, cell D2 should contain "
"<userinput>=B2 * C2</userinput>, D3 should be <userinput>=B3 * C3</"
"userinput>, D4 should be <userinput>=B4 * C4</userinput> and so on. Instead "
"of having to enter a different formula in each cell, you can just enter the "
"first formula into D2 and then copy it into the cells below, letting "
"&sheets; adjust the cell references to suit."
msgstr ""
"Ovo se može činiti kao čudan način kopiranja, ali 99 posto vremena to je ono "
"što želimo (ako nije pogledajte dio o  <link linkend=\"absolute\">absolute "
"cell references</link>). Na primjer u jednostavnoj listi za kupovinu "
"prikazanoj ispod, ćelija D2 treba sadržati <userinput>=B2 * C2</userinput>, "
"D3 treba biti  <userinput>=B3 * C3</userinput>, D4 treba biti <userinput>=B4 "
"* C4</userinput> i tako dalje. Umjesto unosa različitih formula u svaku "
"ćeliju, možete samo unijeti prvu formulu u D2 a onda tu ćeliju kopirati u "
"ćelije ispod, dozvoljavajući &sheets;-u da prilagodi reference tako da "
"odgovaraju."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot copy1"
msgstr "Snimka ekrana copy1"

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copying and Pasting Cell Areas"
msgstr "Kopiranje i Lijepljenje područja ćelija"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the above example D2 can be copied into all three cells D3 to D5 at once "
"by just copying D2 then selecting the complete cell area D3:D5 before doing "
"the paste."
msgstr ""
"U primjerima iznad D2 može biti kopirana u sve tri ćelije D3 do D5 odjednom "
"kopirajući samo D2, a zatim izborom područja ćelija D3:D5 prije lijepljenja."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A rectangular area of cells can be cut or copied in one operation by "
"selecting the area before doing the cut or copy. Then select the top left "
"corner cell of the area you want to paste into before doing the paste."
msgstr ""
"Pravougaono područje ćelija može biti isječeno ili kopirano u jednoj "
"operaciji odabirom područja prije rezanja i kopiranja. Onda odaberite ćeliju "
"u gornjem lijevom uglu područja u koje želite zalijepiti ćeliju."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you cut or copy a rectangular area of cells, say B2:C3, and paste it into "
"a larger area such as A10:D13 the original pattern of cells will be repeated "
"to fill the target area."
msgstr ""
"Ako režete ili kopirate prevougaono područje ćelija, recimo B2:C3 i "
"zalijepite ga u veće područje kao A10:D13 originalni oblik će biti ponavljan "
"da se popuni željeno područje."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; also provides a <quote>Drag and Copy</quote> method for copying "
"cells down into other cells immediately below or to the right of the "
"original cell(s). To use this method select the cell(s) to be copied then "
"position the mouse pointer over the small black square at the bottom right "
"corner of the selected cell(s) so the cursor changes to a double headed "
"arrow. Then hold the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button down while "
"you drag the selected cell(s) as far as you wish. Note that cell references "
"in formulae are incremented according to the relative position change. "
"Absolute references are not changed."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; također omogućuje <quote>Prevuci i kopiraj</quote> metodu za "
"kopiranje ćelija prema dole u ćelije odmah ispod ili lijevo od originalne. "
"Da biste koristili ovaj metod odaberite ćelije za kopiranje a zatim "
"pozicionirajte pokazivač miša iznad malog crnog kvadratića na dnu lijevog "
"ugla pdabranih ćelija tako da pokazivač postane dupla strelica. Onda držite "
"<mousebutton>lijevu</mousebutton> tipku miša dok prevlačite odabrane ćelije "
"koliko daleko želite. Primjetite da se reference u ćelijama mijenjaju prema "
"promjeni pozicije. Apsolutna referenca se ne mijenja."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Paste Modes"
msgstr "Ostale metode lijepljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A cell may contain text, a value, or a formula, and may also contain special "
"font, border or background <link linkend=\"formatspread\">formatting "
"information</link>. &sheets; has special versions of Paste that let you "
"handle these items in different ways."
msgstr ""
"Ćelija može sadržavati tekst, vrijednost, ili formulu, ali također i "
"specijalni font, okvir ili pozadinu <link linkend=\"formatspread"
"\">informacije o formatiranju</link>. &sheets; ima specijalne vrste "
"lijepljenja koje vam dozvoljavaju rad sa ovim stavkama na različite načine."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Special Paste...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>brings up the <guilabel> Special Paste</guilabel> "
"dialog box. By selecting the appropriate item from the left part of this "
"dialog you can choose to paste <guilabel>Everything</guilabel>, just "
"<guilabel>Text</guilabel>, the cell <guilabel>Format</guilabel>, any "
"<guilabel>Comment</guilabel> in the cell(s) or <guilabel>Everything without "
"border</guilabel>. The items in the right part of this dialog box allow you "
"to do simple <link linkend=\"sumspecialpaste\">arithmetic on an area of "
"cells</link>."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Specijalno lijepljenje...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> daje <guilabel> Specijalno lijepljenje</guilabel> "
"okvir. Izborom neke od stavki iz lijevog dijela ovog okvira možete odrediti "
"čta ćete zalijepiti <guilabel>Sve</guilabel>, samo <guilabel>Tekst</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Format</guilabel> ćelije, bilo koji <guilabel>Komentar</"
"guilabel> u ćeliji ili <guilabel>Sve bez okvira</guilabel>. Stavke u desnom "
"dijelu okvira dozvoljavaju vam jednostavnu <link linkend=\"sumspecialpaste"
"\">aritmetiku na području ćelija</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Paste with Insertion...</guimenuitem> inserts the copied "
"cell(s) into the sheet by moving the cells that would otherwise be "
"overwritten a suitable number of rows of columns down or to the right. It "
"can also be used to insert complete copied row(s) or column(s) into the "
"worksheet."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Zalijepi sa umetanjem...</guimenuitem> ubacuje kopirane ćelije "
"u list pomjeranjem ćelija koje bi bile pokrivene određenim brojem redova i "
"kolona dole ili desno. Može biti korišteno i za ubacivanje kompletno "
"kopiranih redova ili kolona u radni list."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert and Delete"
msgstr "Ubaci i obriši"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <keysym>Del</keysym> key or <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Clear</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Contents</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> to remove the text, value or formula from selected cell(s), "
"row(s) or column(s) without affecting anything else."
msgstr ""
"Koristite <keysym>Del</keysym> tipku ili <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Očisti</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Sadržaje</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice> da uklonite tekst, vrijednost ili formulu iz odabranih ćelija, "
"redova ili kolona bez utjecaja na ostalo."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete everything in the selected cell(s), row(s) or column(s), including "
"comments and special formatting, choose the <guimenuitem>All</guimenuitem> "
"option from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Clear</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu or from the pop up menu you get when you "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on a selection."
msgstr ""
"Da biste obrisali sve u odabranim ćelijama redovima ili kolonama, "
"uključujući komentare i specijalno formatiranje, odaberite <guimenuitem>Sve</"
"guimenuitem> opciju iz <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Očisti</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menija ili iz skočnog "
"menija kada pritisnete <mousebutton>desnom</mousebutton> tipkom miša na "
"odabrani dio."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove selected row(s) or column(s) completely, use the "
"<guimenuitem>Delete Rows</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Delete Columns</"
"guimenuitem> options from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button "
"pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Da u potpunosti uklonite odabrane redove ili kolone koristite "
"<guimenuitem>Obriši redove</guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Obriši kolone</"
"guimenuitem> opcije iz skočnog menija <mousebutton>desne</mousebutton> tipke "
"miša."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a cell or cells and choose <guimenuitem>Remove Cells... </"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button pop up "
"menu, you can then choose whether other cells in the worksheet will be moved "
"up or to the left to fill in the space left by the cell(s) you have chosen "
"to remove."
msgstr ""
"Ako odaberete ćeliju ili ćelije i izaberete <guimenuitem>Ukloni ćelije... </"
"guimenuitem> iz skočnog menija <mousebutton>desne</mousebutton> tipke miša, "
"zatim možete odabrati da li će ostale ćelije u radnom listu biti pomaknute "
"prema gore ili lijevo da se popuni prazni prostor ostao iza uklonjenih "
"ćelija."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to insert new, blank, row(s) or column(s) into the sheet, select "
"row(s) or column(s) where you wish the new row(s) or column(s) to be placed "
"and choose the <guimenuitem>Insert Rows</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Insert "
"Columns</guimenuitem> option from the <mousebutton> right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite ubaciti nove prazne, redove ili kolone u list odaberite redove "
"ili kolone gdje želite da budu smješteni novi redovi i kolone i odaberite "
"<guimenuitem>Ubaci redove</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Ubaci kolone</"
"guimenuitem> opciju iz skočnog menija <mousebutton> desne</mousebutton> "
"tipke miša."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert new cells into the worksheet by selecting the area where you "
"want them to appear then choosing the <guimenuitem> Insert Cells...</"
"guimenuitem> option from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button "
"pop up menu. You will then be asked whether the existing cell(s) in the "
"selected area should be moved down or to the right to make room for the new "
"ones."
msgstr ""
"Nove ćelije u radni list možete ubaciti odabirom područja u kojem želite da "
"se pojave i izborom <guimenuitem> Ubaci ćelije...</guimenuitem> opciju iz "
"skočnog menija <mousebutton>desne</mousebutton> tipke miša. Zatim ćete biti "
"pitani da li se trenutne ćelije u odabranom području trebaju biti pomjerene "
"dole ili desno da se napravi prostor za nove ćelije."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Sums"
msgstr "Jednostavne sume"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the first character in a cell is an equals sign (<keycap>=</keycap>) "
"&sheets; will take the cell contents to be a formula which is to be "
"calculated. The result of the calculation will be displayed in the cell "
"rather than the formula itself. For example, enter <userinput>=2+3</"
"userinput> into a cell and it should display <emphasis>5</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Ako je prvi znak u ćeliji znak jednakosti  (<keycap>=</keycap>) &sheets; "
"uzima da je sadržaj ćelije formula koje treba biti izračunata. Rezultat "
"proračuna će biti prikazan u ćeliji prije nego formula. Na primjer unesite "
"<userinput>=2+3</userinput> u ćeliju i ona bi trebala prikazati <emphasis>5</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More usefully, a formula can contain references to other cells, so that "
"<userinput>=B4+A3</userinput> will calculate the sum of the values in cells "
"B4 and A3, and this calculation will be updated whenever cells B4 or A3 are "
"changed."
msgstr ""
"Korisnije , formula može sadržati referencu na druge ćelije tako da "
"<userinput>=B4+A3</userinput> računa sumu vrijednosti u ćelijama B4 i A3, i "
"ovaj proračun će biti osvježen svaki put kada su B4 ili A3 promijenjene."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as addition, a formula can make use of the <keycap>-</keycap> symbol "
"for subtraction, <keycap>*</keycap> for multiplication, and <keycap> /</"
"keycap> to perform division. The round bracket symbols <keycap>(</keycap> "
"and <keycap>)</keycap> can also be used as in normal algebra, so you could "
"enter more complex formulae such as <userinput>=((B10 + C3) *5 - F11) / 2 </"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Kao dodatak formula može koristiti simbol  <keycap>-</keycap> za oduzimanje, "
"<keycap>*</keycap> za množenje  i  <keycap> /</keycap> za dijeljenje. Male "
"zagrade <keycap>(</keycap> i <keycap>)</keycap> mogu biti korištene za "
"normalnu algebru, tako da možete unositi složenije formule kao "
"<userinput>=((B10 + C3) *5 - F11) / 2 </userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cells containing a formula will be marked with a small blue triangle at the "
"bottom left corner if the <guilabel>Show formula indicator</guilabel> check "
"box in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Sheet Properties</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> dialog is "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Ćelije koje sadrže formulu će biti označene sa malim plavim trouglom u "
"donjem lijevom uglu ako je <guilabel>Pokaži indikator formule</guilabel> "
"označen u <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>List</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Osobine lista</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> okviru."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; also includes a large number of built-in functions for applications "
"such as statistical, trigonometrical and financial calculations. Their use "
"will be examined in more depth in a <link linkend=\"formulas\"> later "
"section</link> of this manual, but if you are interested at this stage "
"choose <guimenuitem>Function...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Insert</"
"guimenu> menu and take a look through the <guilabel>Function</guilabel> "
"dialog box that will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; također uključuje veliki broj ugrađenih funkcija za aplikacije kao "
"statističke, trigonometrijske i finansijske proračune. Ovo će detaljnije "
"biti objašnjeno u <link linkend=\"formulas\"> kasnijem odjeljku</link> ovog "
"uputstva, ali ako ste zainteresovani u ovoj fazi odaberite "
"<guimenuitem>Funkcija...</guimenuitem> iz <guimenu>Ubaci</guimenu> menija i "
"pogledajte u <guilabel>Funkcija</guilabel> okviru koji bude prikazan."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the time being, however, the <userinput>SUM</userinput> function may be "
"of interest as it calculates the sum of all values in a specified area of "
"cells. For example <userinput>=SUM(B4:C10)</userinput> calculates the sum of "
"all values in the cell area B4 to C10."
msgstr ""
"Za sada <userinput>SUM</userinput> funkcija može biti od interesa kako ona "
"računa sumu vrijednosti u dijelu ćelija. Na primjer  <userinput>=SUM(B4:"
"C10)</userinput> računa sumu vrijednosti u području ćelija B4 do C10."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &sheets; displays <keycap>#VALUE!</keycap> when you have entered your "
"formula this usually means that it cannot understand what you have entered, "
"but if the row of symbols ends with a small red arrow this just means that "
"the cell is not wide enough to display the complete result, in which case "
"you should either make the cell(s) wider or change their <link linkend="
"\"formatdata\">format</link> so that the result does fit properly."
msgstr ""
"Ako &sheets; ispiše <keycap>#VALUE!</keycap> kada ste unijeli formulu ovo "
"obično znači da ne razumije šta ste unijeli, ali ako red simbola završava sa "
"malom crvenom strelicom ovo samo znači da ćelija nije doboljno velika da "
"prikaže kompletan rezultat, u tom slučaju ili povećajte ćeliju ili "
"promjenite njihov  <link linkend=\"formatdata\">format</link> tako da "
"rezultat pravilno stane."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recalculation"
msgstr "Ponovno izračunavanje"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Automatic recalculation</guilabel> box in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Sheet Properties</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> dialog "
"box is checked, &sheets; will recalculate the values of cells whenever "
"anything that affects them is changed in the sheet."
msgstr ""
"Ako je <guilabel>Automatsko ponovno izračunavanje</guilabel> kvadratić u "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>List</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Osobine lista</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> okviru "
"označen, &sheets; će ponovo izračunati vrijednost u ćelijama kad god je "
"nešto što utiče na njih promijenjeno."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Automatic recalculation</guilabel> is not checked for the "
"current sheet, you can instruct &sheets; to perform a recalculation at any "
"time by using the <guimenuitem>Recalculate Sheet</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem> Recalculate Document</guimenuitem> option in the "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu or their shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;<keysym>F9</keysym> </keycombo> or <keysym>F9</keysym>."
msgstr ""
"Kada <guilabel>Automatsko ponovno izračunavanje</guilabel> kvadratić nije "
"označen za trenutni list, možete zadati  &sheets;-u da radi ponovno "
"izračunavanje u bilo kom trenutku korištenjem <guimenuitem>Ponovo izračunaj "
"list</guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem> Ponovo izračunaj dokument</guimenuitem> "
"opcija u <guimenu>Alati meniju</guimenu> ili njihovim kraticama <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keysym>F9</keysym> </keycombo> ili <keysym>F9</"
"keysym>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting Data"
msgstr "Sortiranje podataka"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the simple example shown below, the data consist of the names and "
"countries of a number of mountains together with their height above sea "
"level. &sheets; can sort data such as this in different ways."
msgstr ""
"U jednostavnom primjeru ispod, podaci se sastoje od imena i država određenog "
"broja planina zajedno sa njihovom nadmorskom visinom. &sheets; može "
"sortirati podatke na više načina."

#. Tag: phrase
#: basics.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of sorted data"
msgstr "Snimak ekrana sortiranih podataka"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We may want the data sorted so that the names are in alphabetical order. To "
"do this select the area containing the data (A2:C7 in this case) and choose "
"<guimenuitem>Sort...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Data</guimenu> menu. "
"This opens the <guilabel>Sort</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Možda želimo podatke sortirati tako da su imena u abecednom redu. Da uradite "
"ovo odaberite ćelije sa podacima (A2:C7 u ovom slučaju) i odaberite "
"<guimenuitem>Sortiraj...</guimenuitem> iz <guimenu>Podaci</guimenu> menija. "
"Ovo otvara <guilabel>Sortiraj</guilabel> okvir."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sorting is done alphanumerically, and the default is case sensitive, numbers "
"coming before uppercase letters which come before lowercase letters, so that "
"cells containing the entries <userinput>Cat</userinput>, <userinput>bar</"
"userinput>, <userinput>77</userinput> and <userinput>Bat</userinput> would "
"be sorted into the following order: <emphasis>77 Bat Cat bar</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Sortiranje se obavlja abecedno, a zadano je osjetljivo na velika i mala "
"slova, brojevi dolaze prije velikih slova koja dolaze ispred malih slova, "
"tako da ćelija koja sadrži unose <userinput>Cat</userinput>, <userinput>bar</"
"userinput>, <userinput>77</userinput> and <userinput>Bat</userinput> biti "
"sortirana u slijedećem redoslijedu: <emphasis>77 Bat Cat bar</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Direction</guilabel> area of this dialog box select to sort "
"in rows or columns. If you check the <guilabel>First row contains column "
"headers</guilabel> or <guilabel>First column contains row headers</guilabel> "
"box data in the first row or column will not be included in the sort "
"operation."
msgstr ""
"U <guilabel>Pravac</guilabel> području ovog okvira odaberite sortiranje "
"redova ili kolona. Ako označite <guilabel>Prvi red sadrži naslove kolona</"
"guilabel> ili <guilabel>Prva kolona sadrži naslove redova</guilabel> okvire "
"u prvom redu neće biti uključeno sortiranje."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The rows or columns are sorted in the specified order, which can be changed "
"using the <guibutton>Move Up</guibutton> and <guibutton>Move Down</"
"guibutton> buttons. Using the example in the above screenshot, choosing "
"column B as the first key and column C as the second would sort the data by "
"country and, for each country, by height."
msgstr ""
"Redovi i kolone su sortirane u poseban red, koji može biti promijenjen "
"korištenjem <guibutton>Pomjeri gore</guibutton> and <guibutton>Pomjeri dole</"
"guibutton> tipki. Korištenjem primjera u snimci ekrana iznad izborom kolone "
"B kao prvu tipku i kolone C kao drugu će sortirati podatke po državi i za "
"svaku državu po visini."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uncheck the option <guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel> to get a sort not "
"depending on capitalization and switch the sort order between "
"<guilabel>Ascending</guilabel> and <guilabel>Descending</guilabel> by "
"clicking on the cells in the column <guilabel>Sort Order</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Odznačite opciju <guilabel>Osjetljivo na veličinu slova</guilabel> da "
"dobijete sortiranje nezavisno od veličine slova i mijenjate red sortiranja "
"između <guilabel>Rastućeg</guilabel> i <guilabel>Opadajućeg</guilabel> "
"pritiskom na ćelije u koloni <guilabel>Red sortiranja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Details >></guilabel> extension of the dialog allows you to "
"sort using the order of items in a custom list such as January, February... "
"instead of alphanumerically. The cell format is moved with the cell content, "
"if you select <guilabel>Copy cell formatting (Borders, Colors, Text Style)</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Detalji >></guilabel> proširenje okvira dozvoljava vam sortiranje "
"korištenjem poretka stavki u uređenoj listi kao Januar, Februar... umjesto "
"alfanumeričkog. Format ćelije je pomjeren sa ćelijom ako odaberete "
"<guilabel>Kopiraj formatiranje ćelije (Okvire, Boje, Stil teksta)</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Status bar Summary Calculator"
msgstr "Statusna traka rezime kalkulatora"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left hand end of the Status bar by default shows a summary of the values "
"in the selected cell(s). According to the setting of the <guilabel>Function "
"shown in status bar</guilabel> combo box in the <guilabel>Interface</"
"guilabel> page of &sheets;'s configuration dialog the summary can be:"
msgstr ""
"Lijevi dio Statusne trake zadano prikazuje rezime vrijednosti u odabranim "
"ćelijama. Prema postavkama <guilabel>Funkcije prikazane u statusnoj traci</"
"guilabel> kutiji <guilabel>Okruženje</guilabel> stranice u  &sheets;-u okvir "
"sa podešavanjima rezimea može biti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Nikakav"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "No summary calculation is performed."
msgstr "Nema kalkulacija rezimea."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Average"
msgstr "Prosječan"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the average of the values in the selected cells."
msgstr "Prikazana je prosječna vrijednost vrijednosti u odabranim ćelijama."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Count"
msgstr "Brojač"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the number of cells containing numeric values."
msgstr "Prikazana vrijednost je broj ćelija sa numeričkim vrijednostima."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "CountA"
msgstr "BrojačA"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the number of non empty cells."
msgstr "Prikazana je broj ćelija koje nisu prazne."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Max</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Maksimum</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the maximum of the values in the selected cells."
msgstr "Prikazana je maksimalna vrijednost u odabranim ćelijama."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Min</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Minimum</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the minimum of the values in the selected cells."
msgstr "Prikazana je minimalna vrijednost u odabranim ćelijama."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: basics.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Sum</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Suma</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "The value displayed is the sum of the values in the selected cells."
msgstr "Prikazana je suma vrijednosti u odabranim ćelijama."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The method of calculation can also be changed by <mousebutton>right </"
"mousebutton> clicking on the summary calculation result area of the Status "
"bar and choosing an item from the pop up menu."
msgstr ""
"Način izračunavanja može biti promijenjen <mousebutton>desnim </mousebutton> "
"pritiskom na rezime kalkulacije područje sa rezultatom u Statusnoj traci i "
"izborom stavke iz skočnog menija."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving your Work"
msgstr "Spremanje vašeg rada"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; saves the complete document, which may include more than one "
"worksheet, as a single document file."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; sprema cijeli dokument, koji može uključivati više od jednog radnog "
"lista, kao jeda dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have created a new document, or want to save an existing one under a "
"different name, use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem> Save "
"As...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will bring up &kde;'s common "
"<guilabel>Save Document As</guilabel> dialog box. Choose the folder where "
"you want to save the document and enter a suitable file name into the "
"<guilabel>Name</guilabel> text box. &sheets; documents are normally "
"automatically saved with a <filename>.ods</filename> extension, you do not "
"need to add this to the filename but do make sure that the <guilabel>Filter</"
"guilabel> selection is set to <guilabel>OpenDocument SpreadSheet</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste kreirali novi dokument, ili želite spremiti postojeći pod drugim "
"imenom, koristite <menuchoice><guimenu>Dokument</guimenu><guimenuitem> "
"Spremi kao...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ovo će otvoriti &kde;-ov "
"standardni <guilabel>Spremi dokument kao</guilabel> okvir. Odaberite folder "
"u koji želite spremiti dokument i unesite odgovarajuće ime dokumenta u  "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel> tekstualni okvir. &sheets; dokumenti su automatski "
"sačuvani u <filename>.ods</filename> formatu, ne morate ovo dodavati imenu "
"dokumenta ali se uvjerite da je <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> odjeljak "
"postavljen na <guilabel>Otvori dokument tabelarni proračun</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To save your document without changing its name, just use <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"DA sačuvate vaš dokument bez mijenjanja imena, samo koristite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Dokument</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spremi</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also save a &sheets; document in a foreign format selecting the "
"format from the <guilabel>Filter:</guilabel> combo box."
msgstr ""
"Možete spremiti &sheets; dokument i u drugom formatu izborom formata u "
"<guilabel>Filter:</guilabel> kutiji."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you save a modified version of an existing document &sheets; will keep "
"the previous version as a backup file, adding a <literal>~</literal> to the "
"end of the filename."
msgstr ""
"Kada spremite izmijenjenu verziju postojećeg dokumenta  &sheets; zadržava "
"prethodnu verziju kao dokument podrške dodavajući <literal>~</literal> na "
"kraj imena dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; can provide some protection against losing your work because of a "
"computer crash or because you have closed &sheets; without saving the "
"current document. It does this by automatically saving the latest version of "
"the document you are working on every few minutes using a modified file "
"name. The autosaved version is normally removed when you next save your "
"document, so that it will only exist if it is more up to date than the "
"version that was saved manually. When you open a document &sheets; checks to "
"see if an autosaved version exists, and if it finds one it will offer to "
"open that instead."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; može omogućiti neku zaštitu od gubljenja podataka pri gašenju "
"računara ili zatvaranja &sheets;-a bez spremanja trenutnog dokumenta. Ovo se "
"radi automatskim spremanjem posljednje verzije dokumenta na kojem radite "
"svakih pet minuta korištenjem izmjenjenog imena dokumenta. Auto spremljena "
"verzija je normalno uklonjena kada vi spremite vaš dokument, tako da sao "
"postoji ako je novija od posljednje ručno spremljene verzije. Kada otvarate "
"dokument &sheets; provjerava da li suto spremljena verzija postoji i ako "
"nađe neku ponudiće vam da je otvorite."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Autosaved documents are saved with a file name of the form <filename>."
"yourfilename.autosave</filename> (note the leading period), so that "
"<filename>spread1.ods</filename> would be autosaved as <filename>.spread1."
"ods.autosave</filename>. The autosave feature is user configurable in the "
"<link linkend=\"configopensave\">settings dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Auto spremljeni dokumenti se spremaju s imenom u formi <filename>."
"imedokumenta.autosave</filename> (primjetite početnu tačku), tako da "
"<filename>spread1.ods</filename> bi bio spremljen kao <filename>.spread1.ods."
"autosave</filename>. Dodatak za auto spremanje korisnik može podešavati u "
"<link linkend=\"configopensave\">okviru sa postavkama</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Templates"
msgstr "Šabloni"

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are going to be creating a lot of similar documents you can save "
"yourself time and trouble by first creating a template and then using that "
"as the basis for the individual documents."
msgstr ""
"Ako ćete kreirati mnogo sličnih dokumenata možete sebi uštediti vrijeme i "
"trud i prvo kreirati šablon i koristiti ga kao osnovu za pojedinačne "
"dokumente."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do this first create a document containing the common elements, then save "
"it as a template by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Create Template From Document</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Doing "
"this opens the <guilabel>Create Template</guilabel> dialog box. Enter a name "
"for your new template into the <guilabel>Name:</guilabel> text box and press "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>. The next time you start a new document by "
"choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or when you next start &sheets; the startup dialog window will "
"give you the option of creating the new document from your template."
msgstr ""
"Da biste to uradili kreirajte dokument koji sadrži zajedničke elemente, onda "
"ga spremite kao šablon izborom <menuchoice><guimenu>Dokument</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kreirajte šablon iz dokumenta</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. AKo "
"ovo uradite otvoriće se <guilabel>Kreiraj šablon</guilabel> okvir. Unesite "
"ime vašeg šablona u  <guilabel>Ime :</guilabel> tekstualni okvir i "
"pritisnite <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. Slijedeći put kada pokrenete novi "
"dokument izborom  <menuchoice><guimenu>Dokument</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novi</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ili kada pokrenete  &sheets; početni prozor će vam "
"dati opciju kreiranja novog dokumenta sa vašim šablonom,."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Create Template</guilabel> dialog box also lets you choose a "
"different picture to be displayed above the template name in the startup "
"dialog window, and lets you save your templates under different group names, "
"which will appear as different pages in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kreiraj šablon</guilabel> okvir omogućava izbor različite slike "
"koja će biti prikazana iznad imena šablona u početnom prozoru, i dozvoljava "
"vam da spremite vaše pablone pod različitim grupnim imenima, koja će se "
"pojaviti kao različite stranice u okviru."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Templates are stored as <literal role=\"extension\">.kst</literal> files "
"under <filename>~/.kde/share/apps/tables/templates/</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Šabloni su spremljeni kao <literal role=\"extension\">.kst</literal> "
"dokumenti u <filename>~/.kde/share/apps/tables/templates/</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: basics.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing a Spreadsheet"
msgstr "Štampanje tabelarnih proračuna."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Printing a spreadsheet is basically done by selecting <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"which brings up &kde;'s common <guilabel>Print</guilabel> dialog box where "
"you can choose, among other options, the printer to be used, the number of "
"copies and whether all or only selected pages are to be printed."
msgstr ""
"Štampanje tabelarnog proračuna se vrši izborom <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Dokument</guimenu><guimenuitem>Štampaj...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> koji daje standardni  &kde;-ov <guilabel>Štampanje</guilabel> "
"okvir gdje možete odabrati, među opcijama, koji će štampač biti korišten, "
"broj kopija i trebaju li sve ili samo odabrane stranice biti štampane."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &sheets; will print all items in the current worksheet, but you "
"can restrict this by first selecting the area that you want to be printed "
"then choosing <guimenuitem>Define Print Range</guimenuitem> from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Print Range</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> sub menu."
msgstr ""
"Zadano &sheets;  štampa sve stavke u trenutnom radnom listu, ali ovo možete "
"zabraniti izborom područja koje želite štampati a zatim izborom "
"<guimenuitem>Definiši opseg štampanja</guimenuitem> iz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Opseg štampanja</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> pod menija."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; will print as many pages as are necessary to include all items in "
"the current worksheet. You can quickly see how a worksheet will be split "
"into separate pages for printing by checking the <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Page Borders</guimenuitem></menuchoice> box. The "
"boundaries of each printed page will then be marked by colored lines in the "
"worksheet."
msgstr ""
"&sheets; štampa onoliko stranica koliko je potrebno da se uključe sve stavke "
"u trenutnom radnom listu. Možete brzo pregledati kako će radni list biti "
"podijeljen u odvojene stranice za printanje označavanjem <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Vidi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Okviri stranice</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Okviri svake stranice za štampanje će onda biti označeni "
"obojenim linijama u radnom listu."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a more detailed view of what is to be sent to the printer, including "
"anything you have asked to be included in the page headers and footers (see "
"below), choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print "
"Preview...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Za detaljniji pregled šta će biti poslano na štampanje, uključujući sve što "
"ste tražili da bude uključeno u naslove stranica i fusnote (vidjeti ispod) "
"odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Dokument</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pregled prije "
"štampanja...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To improve the appearance of the printed output , you can change the fonts, "
"colors, borders and sizes of the cells in the worksheet, see the <link "
"linkend=\"formatspread\">Spreadsheet Formatting</link> section for more "
"details about how to do this."
msgstr ""
"Da poboljšate izgled izlaza iz štampača, možete promijeniti font, boje, "
"okvire i veličinu ćelija u radnom listu, pogledajte <link linkend="
"\"formatspread\">Formatiranje tabelarnih proračuna</link>  odjeljku za više "
"detalja kako ovo uraditi."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guilabel>Page Layout</guilabel> dialog box, invoked by "
"selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Page Layout...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, to change the orientation of the printed pages, "
"the paper size (this should be suitable for your printer) and the size of "
"the page borders."
msgstr ""
"Također možete koristiti <guilabel>Položaj stranice</guilabel> okvir, pozvan "
"izborom <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Položaj stranice..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da promijenite orijentaciju štampanih stranica, "
"veličinu papira (ovo treba odgovarati štampaču) i veličini okvira papira."

#. Tag: para
#: basics.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Sheet</guilabel> provides more options. The <guilabel>Print "
"settings</guilabel> section lets you select whether or not to print the "
"grid, comment indicators and formula indicators, objects and charts. The "
"<guilabel>Repetitions on each page</guilabel> section allows you to repeat "
"selected column(s) or row(s) on each printed page. In the section "
"<guilabel>Scaling</guilabel> you can set a scalefactor or the page limits "
"for the print."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>List</guilabel> daje više opcija. <guilabel>Postavke štampanja</"
"guilabel> odjeljak dozvoljava izbor da li će se štampati ivice, prikazi "
"komentara i formula, objekti i grafikoni. <guilabel>Ponavljanja na svakoj "
"stranici</guilabel> odjeljak vam dozvoljava da ponovite odabrane kolone ili "
"redovi na svakoj štampanoj stranici. U ovom odjeljku <guilabel>Skaliranje</"
"guilabel> možete podesiti faktor skaliranja ili ograničenja po stranicama za "
"štampanje."
